===Etymology===
From {{etyl|grc}} {{term|ἀποθέωσις|sc=polytonic}}, from verb {{term|ἀποθεόω||deify|sc=polytonic}} (factitive verb formed from {{term|θεός||God|sc=polytonic}} with intensive prefix {{term|ἀπο-|sc=polytonic}}).

